    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/366af5911ebc699fdd0f7d6cfdeede5b.poster.avif?t=1745970599\" width=632 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/366af5911ebc699fdd0f7d6cfdeede5b.webm?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/cae47c78df0a2c593b1275c4f5314366.poster.avif?t=1745970599\" width=632 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/cae47c78df0a2c593b1275c4f5314366.webm?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/cae47c78df0a2c593b1275c4f5314366.mp4?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>欢迎来到《D.O.T.攻防战》， 一个简化但具有深度策略性的实施战略游戏。简化的经济系统、大规模的自动战斗与轻量化指挥，以及一个有趣易用的升级系统，让我们的游戏既易上手又具有战术深度。5-10分钟就能完成一局紧张刺激的游戏体验！<br><br>通往胜利的唯一目标是保护你的总部并摧毁敌方部队！我们的游戏由热爱实施战略的开发者精心打造，旨在从他们的童年回忆中带给你令人怀念的经典体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《D.O.T.攻防战》的Demo版包含：</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>两张地图：每种模式下都有两张地图。<br></li><li>混战模式：最多支持4人（玩家或AI）混战。<br></li><li>波次防御模式：与数量逐渐递增的敌方军队奋战到底，在每波中解锁新的领地和地块！<br></li><li>教学模式：学习基础游戏机制。<br></li><li>游戏音乐：充盈活力鼓点和贝斯的背景音乐集。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >请注意：此Demo版是游戏完整版的预览。如果你玩得开心，请加入我们的Discord，并且考虑将本作加入你的Steam游戏愿望单！</h2></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/fddb38b359522c1a5010465a23732828.apng?t=1745970599\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/fddb38b359522c1a5010465a23732828.poster.avif?t=1745970599\" class=\"bb_img\" width=632 height=64 /></picture></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/1d9f588ebb49598ba4389a13a49e84b0.poster.avif?t=1745970599\" width=632 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/1d9f588ebb49598ba4389a13a49e84b0.webm?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/1d9f588ebb49598ba4389a13a49e84b0.mp4?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >炮塔混战</h2><br>你的领地是发展经济的命脉；使用各种炮塔抵御敌方部队的层层进攻、保护你的资源。每种炮塔都代表不同的战略选择，合理搭配运用、回收来调整出适合挑战场景的战术！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/d22d25fd789f34be24b837d98eda1254.poster.avif?t=1745970599\" width=632 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/d22d25fd789f34be24b837d98eda1254.webm?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/d22d25fd789f34be24b837d98eda1254.mp4?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >波次防御</h2><br>建造炮塔和生产设施来誓死保卫你的总部。在遭遇战模式中，你会获得更加接近传统即时战略游戏的体验。但也别忘了试试波次防御模式！在这个模式中，你会逐渐拓展你的领地，收集物资升级区域，并战略性地在各处部署炮塔来抵御意想不到的进攻。你甚至可能会遇到战地商人，在战场上售卖具有增幅建筑效果的特殊地块！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/c830c6c8ee1e56eb5a12fe5e3a7ac4fb.poster.avif?t=1745970599\" width=632 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/c830c6c8ee1e56eb5a12fe5e3a7ac4fb.webm?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/c830c6c8ee1e56eb5a12fe5e3a7ac4fb.mp4?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >指挥官扮演</h2><br>通过简单易用的宏观命令来指挥作战单位的行军路线、或者指引他们自动抢占关键作战位置。在《D.O.T.攻防战》中，体验易上手与深策略的结合！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/38e6d7fdcd07d6904f399e955926eefe.poster.avif?t=1745970599\" width=632 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/38e6d7fdcd07d6904f399e955926eefe.webm?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/38e6d7fdcd07d6904f399e955926eefe.mp4?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本地多人混战</h2><br>召集朋友们来局紧张的1v1、2v2吧！每个决策都至关重要。不管你是经验丰富的战略家，还是即时战略的新手，《D.O.T.攻防战》都会为你提供适应你熟练度的刺激玩法。我们的AI有循序渐进的难度（是的，有一个会开挂的！）<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/c85f97c80a7ea2bb27e4a8ed4c2888f5.poster.avif?t=1745970599\" width=632 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/c85f97c80a7ea2bb27e4a8ed4c2888f5.webm?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/c85f97c80a7ea2bb27e4a8ed4c2888f5.mp4?t=1745970599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >休闲乐趣！</h2><br>《D.O.T.攻防战》将易上手的玩法与策略深度结合，非常适合喜欢本地多人游戏的玩家。指挥你的部队、征服整个地图，然后在这段刺激的即时战略冒险中夺得胜利的桂冠吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/fddb38b359522c1a5010465a23732828.apng?t=1745970599\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134200/extras/fddb38b359522c1a5010465a23732828.poster.avif?t=1745970599\" class=\"bb_img\" width=632 height=64 /></picture></span>",
